OL,5,G1955 Grand Designs
OL,6,     FAfter recovering from a brain
OL,7,     Fhaemorrhage, Bram Vis and his wife
OL,8,     FLisa want to build a beautiful,
OL,9,     Fcutting-edge family house on the
OL,10,     FIsle of Wight. But the budget
OL,11,     Fstarts to spiral...
OL,12,G2100 Bill Bailey's Vietnam
OL,13,     FIn Ho Chi Minh City, the most
OL,14,     Fpopulous city in Vietnam, Bill is
OL,15,     Fcaught between wartime tunnels,
OL,16,     Fendless crazy traffic, and a deep
OL,17,     Fdive into a local musical twist of
OL,18,     Fmetal versus folk. (Ep2)
