OL,5,G0020 24 Hours in A&E
OL,6,     FWilliam has broken his leg in
OL,7,     Fthree places. Nick's fallen from a
OL,8,     F10-metre ladder onto concrete. And
OL,9,     FWilfred, who lives alone, has had
OL,10,     Fa nasty accident while cutting
OL,11,     Fvegetables.
OL,12,G0120 999: On the Front Line
OL,13,     FParamedics treat a woman with
OL,14,     Fbrittle bone disease who's had a
OL,15,     Ffall, a young man on the verge of
OL,16,     Fa diabetic coma, and a man who
OL,17,     Fthey have to detain under the
OL,18,     FMental Capacity Act.
